column5: Not to sure f its a rumour or not, but I  hear there was a 50 inch sturgeon caught in the big Creek near Delhi....Anyone hear about this or is it Bull?    Edited to ask mods to correct spelling issue in the title...DOH!
Seen that on the Long Point page, actually 2, but they figure it was the same fish caught twice
